RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, B.USER_REF_NO, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.COUNTERPARTY, B.FACILITY_NAME, A.CONTRACT_CCY, (SELECT CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY) CUST_NAME, (SELECT PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE) PROD_DESC FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER B, OLTB_CONTRACT A WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'C' AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.BRANCH = :GLOBAL.SM_CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS NOT IN ('V','L') AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'LS' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE AND BRANCH_CODE = :GLOBAL.SM_CURRENT_BRANCH AND USER_ID = :GLOBAL.SM_CURRENT_USERID)

SELECT E.ENTITY_CODE, E.ENTITY_DESC, E.ENTITY_TYPE FROM LBTMS_COLLATERAL_ENTITY E WHERE (E.ENTITY_TYPE=:BLK_LSTMS_COLLENT_COLL.COLLATERAL_CODE OR E.ENTITY_TYPE='COLLATERALENTITY') AND E.RECORD_STAT ='O' AND E.AUTH_STAT='A' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTMS_TRANCHE_COLLENT_ENTITY WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO =:BLK_LSTMS_COLLENT_EFFDATE.TRANCHE_REF_NO AND EFFECTIVE_DATE =:BLK_LSTMS_COLLENT_EFFDATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE AND COLLATERAL_CODE =:BLK_LSTMS_COLLENT_COLL.COLLATERAL_CODE AND ENTITY_CODE = E.ENTITY_CODE)

SELECT A.COLLATERAL_CODE,A.COLLATERAL_DESC FROM LBTMS_COLLATERAL A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT ='O' AND A.AUTH_STAT='A' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTM_TRANCHE_COLLENT_COLL WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO =:BLK_LSTMS_COLLENT_EFFDATE.TRANCHE_REF_NO AND EFFECTIVE_DATE =:BLK_LSTMS_COLLENT_EFFDATE.EFFECTIVE_DATE AND COLLATERAL_CODE =A.COLLATERAL_CODE)
